  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070214070854/http://www.defenselink.mil/speeches/speech.aspx?speechid=1123
  | dead-url = no
  }}</ref>，普京亦指俄羅斯不想和美國及西方勢力對抗，只希望美國進行對話及承認雙方的利益平等<ref name="Int_G8_2007">
