== 與中東和北非國家的關係 ==
[[File:Vladimir_Putin_and_Muammar_Gaddafi_in_Moscow_1_Nov_2008-1.jpeg|180px]]實際最高領導人[[奥马尔·穆阿迈尔·卡扎菲|奥马尔·穆阿迈尔·卡扎菲]]上校，攝於2008年]]
於2007年10月16日，普京到[[伊朗|伊朗]][[德黑蘭|德黑蘭]]參加第二屆里海峰會<ref name=rbc-iran-tehran>[https://web.archive.org/web/20080406094726/http://top.rbc.ru/politics/16/10/2007/122607.shtml Putin: Iran Has Right to Develop Peaceful Nuclear Programme], 16 October 2007, Rbc.ru</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Putin's warning to the U.S. |agency=Reuters |date=16 October 2007 |url=http://www.reuters.com/news/video/videoStory?videoId=68897 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071017065727/http://www.reuters.com/news/video/videoStory?videoId=68897 |archivedate=2007-10-17|deadurl=yes }}</ref>，並會見了[[伊朗總統|伊朗總統]][[內賈德|內賈德]]<ref>[http://president.kremlin.ru/text/news/2007/10/148432.shtml Putin Positive on Second Caspian Summit Results, Meets With Iranian President Mahmoud Ahmadinejad] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080504052206/http://president.kremlin.ru/text/news/2007/10/148432.shtml |date=2008-05-04 }}, 16 October 2007, Kremlin.ru</ref>，而峰會其他參與者包括[[阿塞拜疆|阿塞拜疆]]、[[哈薩克斯坦|哈薩克斯坦]]和[[土庫曼斯坦|土庫曼斯坦]]的領導人<ref>[http://president.kremlin.ru/events/chron/2007/10/148247.shtml Visit to Iran. Second Caspian Summit] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080504052159/http://president.kremlin.ru/events/chron/2007/10/148247.shtml |date=2008-05-04 }}, 15–16 October 2007, Kremlin.ru</ref>；在峰會結束後的新聞發布會上，普京指所有的里海國家有發展和平核計劃的權利<ref>[http://president.kremlin.ru/eng/speeches/2007/10/16/2020_type82914type82915_148460.shtml Answer to a Question at the Joint Press Conference Following the Second Caspian Summit] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080504052153/http://president.kremlin.ru/eng/speeches/2007/10/16/2020_type82914type82915_148460.shtml |date=2008-05-04 }}, 16 October 2007, Tehran, Kremlin.ru</ref>。普京曾描述伊朗為“合作夥伴”，但表達了對伊朗核計劃的擔憂<ref name=Sturmer/>。

2008年4月，普京訪問[[利比亞|利比亞]]並會見領導人[[卡扎菲|卡扎菲]]，是首名訪問利比亞的俄羅斯總統，他指在這次訪問中找到了對俄羅斯和利比亞經濟有益的方案<ref>{{cite web |url=http://gulfnews.com/news/region/libya/putin-s-visit-historic-and-strategic-1.98399 |title=Putin's visit 'historic and strategic' |publisher=gulfnews |date=2008-04-18 |accessdate=2013-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130514014600/http://gulfnews.com/news/region/libya/putin-s-visit-historic-and-strategic-1.98399 |archive-date=2013-05-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，又譴責外國軍事干預利比亞，指聯合國決議有缺陷，並指軍事干預像中世紀的[[十字軍東征|十字軍東征]]<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/03/21/putin-libya-intervention-_n_838293.html | work=Huffington Post | first=Cara | last=Parks | title=Putin: Military Intervention In Libya Resembles 'Crusades' | date=21 March 2011 | accessdate=2014-08-02 | archive-date=2014-03-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140328063831/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/03/21/putin-libya-intervention-_n_838293.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[卡扎菲之死|卡扎菲之死]]後，普京指美國策劃謀殺卡扎菲，又指「他們（美國）向整個世界展示他（卡扎菲）如何被打死和到處是血。難道這就是他們所謂的民主嗎？」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mediaite.com/online/vladimir-putin-blames-us-drones-for-gaddafi-death-slams-john-mccain/ |title=Vladimir Putin Blames US Drones For Gaddafi Death, Slams John McCain |publisher=Mediaite |date=2011-12-15 |accessdate=2013-06-22 |archive-date=2012-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120104145441/http://www.mediaite.com/online/vladimir-putin-blames-us-drones-for-gaddafi-death-slams-john-mccain/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Citizen |first=Ottawa |url=http://canada.com/ottawacitizen/news/world/story.html?id=883c4e8f-cd01-4705-b446-fe9c72d3a291 |title=Putin claims U.S. planned murder of Gadhafi |publisher=Canada.com |date=2011-12-16 |accessdate=2013-06-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020152422/http://www.canada.com/ottawacitizen/news/world/story.html?id=883c4e8f-cd01-4705-b446-fe9c72d3a291 |archivedate=2013-10-20 }}</ref>。

{{link-en|迪米特里·特列寧|Dmitri Trenin}}曾在[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]上指，俄羅斯在2000至2010年向[[敘利亞|敘利亞]]銷售了價值約為150億美元的軍火，大馬士革更是莫斯科的第七大客戶<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/10/opinion/why-russia-supports-assad.html?_r=2&partner=rss&emc=rss | work=The New York Times | first=Dmitri | last=Trenin | title=Why Russia Supports Assad | date=9 February 2012 | accessdate=2014-08-02 | archive-date=2015-06-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150611010048/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/10/opinion/why-russia-supports-assad.html?_r=2&partner=rss&emc=rss | dead-url=no }}</ref>；在[[敘利亞內戰|敘利亞內戰]]期間，俄羅斯威脅要否決對敘利亞的任何制裁<ref>{{cite web |author=Fred Weir |url=http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Europe/2012/0119/Why-Russia-is-willing-to-sell-arms-to-Syria |title=Why Russia is willing to sell arms to Syria |publisher=CSMonitor.com |date=2012-01-19 |accessdate=2013-06-22 |archive-date=2013-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130620113131/http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Europe/2012/0119/Why-Russia-is-willing-to-sell-arms-to-Syria |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並繼續提供武器。普京反對任何外國干預敘利亞內政：2012年6月1日，普京拒絕了[[法國總統|法國總統]][[弗朗索瓦·奧朗德|弗朗索瓦·奧朗德]]呼籲[[巴沙爾|巴沙爾]]下台的聲明，並指反政府武裝組織造成大部分的傷亡<ref>{{cite web |last=Viscusi |first=Gregory |url=http://www.businessweek.com/news/2012-06-01/hollande-clashes-with-putin-over-ouster-of-syria-s-assad |title=Hollande Clashes With Putin Over Ouster of Syria’s Assad |publisher=Businessweek |date=2012-06-01 |accessdate=2013-06-22 |archive-date=2013-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130530203815/http://www.businessweek.com/news/2012-06-01/hollande-clashes-with-putin-over-ouster-of-syria-s-assad |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 與前[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]國家的關係 ==
{{see also|顏色革命|歐亞經濟聯盟}}
在一些前蘇聯國家曾發生「顏色革命」，分別為2003年[[格魯吉亞|格魯吉亞]][[玫瑰革命|玫瑰革命]]、[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]][[橙色革命|橙色革命]]及2004及2005年[[吉爾吉斯斯坦|吉爾吉斯斯坦]][[鬱金香革命|鬱金香革命]]，導致這些國家和普京領導下的俄羅斯發生摩擦<ref name=blueandorange/>。2004年12月，普京批評玫瑰革命和橙色革命，指這些革命令前蘇聯地區前陷入無盡的衝突<ref name=blueandorange>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/4122721.stm Polish head rejects Putin attack] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/4122721.stm |date=20140813131549 }}, [[BBC_News|BBC News]] (24 December 2004)</ref>。

2008年8月，[[格魯吉亞總統|格魯吉亞總統]][[薩卡什維利|薩卡什維利]]試圖恢復在[[南奧塞梯|南奧塞梯]]的控制，聲稱此舉是為了回應南奧塞梯對格魯吉亞邊境的襲擊。駐紮在那裡的俄羅斯維和部隊和南奧塞梯並肩作戰，對付格魯吉亞軍隊，並把衝突推進到全省<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.heritage.org/research/RussiaandEurasia/wm2017.cfm |title=Russia and Eurasia |publisher=Heritage.org |accessdate=2009-05-10 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5h7JPwfdR?url=http://www.heritage.org/research/RussiaandEurasia/wm2017.cfm |archivedate=2009-05-28 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/7551576.stm|title=Day-by-day: Georgia-Russia crisis|publisher=BBC News|date=21 August 2008|accessdate=2009-05-10|archive-date=2010-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100420213426/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/7551576.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在這種衝突期間，法國外交官{{link-en|讓-達維德·萊維特|Jean-David Levitte}}指普京打算推翻薩卡什維利<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-1085468/Putin-planned-topple-president-Georgia-hang-b---says-Nicolas-Sarkozys-chief-adviser.html|title=Putin planned to topple the president of Georgia and 'hang him by the b****', says Nicolas Sarkozy's chief adviser|work=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]|date=14 November 2008|location=London|first=Ian|last=Sparks|accessdate=2014-08-02|archive-date=2014-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140903154423/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-1085468/Putin-planned-topple-president-Georgia-hang-b---says-Nicolas-Sarkozys-chief-adviser.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。普京指責格魯吉亞當局的政策造成兩國惡劣的關係，又指格魯吉亞是一個「兄弟國家」，希望他們能明白俄羅斯不是敵人而是朋友<ref>[http://rt.com/politics/russia-friendly-relations-georgia-953/ Putin warns US against rearming Georgia] {{Wayback|url=http://rt.com/politics/russia-friendly-relations-georgia-953/ |date=20140813003313 }}, [[RT_(TV_network)|RT]] (22 February 2012)</ref>；一個月前，格魯吉亞總統薩卡什維利曾表示普京不是與格魯吉亞政府有相處上的問題，而是和格魯吉亞人不和<ref>[http://en.rian.ru/russia/20120121/170877003.html Georgia’s Saakashvili Slams Putin for Nationalist Comment] {{Wayback|url=http://en.rian.ru/russia/20120121/170877003.html |date=20130731093404 }}, [[RIA_Novosti|RIA Novosti]] (21 January 2012)</ref>。

儘管俄羅斯和大部分前蘇聯國家曾有過緊張局勢，普京實施[[歐亞一體化|歐亞一體化]]的政策，而[[白俄羅斯|白俄羅斯]]、哈薩克斯坦和俄羅斯的關稅同盟亦帶來了三個國家的局部經濟統一<ref>[http://www.america-russia.net/eng/geopolitics/288470359 New Integration Project for Eurasia – A Future That Is Being Born Today] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130604193552/http://www.america-russia.net/eng/geopolitics/288470359 |date=2013-06-04 }}, [[Izvestiya|Izvestiya]] (October 3, 2011) {{en icon}}</ref><ref>[http://www.izvestia.ru/news/502761 Новый интеграционный проект для Евразии – будущее, которое рождается сегодня] {{Wayback|url=http://www.izvestia.ru/news/502761 |date=20200615211114 }} {{ru icon}}</ref><ref name=yahoo-reuters>{{cite news|title=Russia's Putin says wants to build "Eurasian Union" |first=Gleb |last=Bryanski |url=http://news.yahoo.com/russias-putin-says-wants-build-eurasian-union-222139037.html |publisher=[[Yahoo!_News|Yahoo! News]] |agency=[[Reuters|Reuters]] |date=3 October 2011 |accessdate=4 October 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111006174652/http://news.yahoo.com/russias-putin-says-wants-build-eurasian-union-222139037.html |archivedate=2011-10-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Новый интеграционный проект для Евразии – будущее, которое рождается сегодня|url=http://www.izvestia.ru/news/502761|newspaper=[[Izvestia|Izvestia]]|language=ru|date=3 October 2011|accessdate=4 October 2011|archive-date=2020-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200615211114/https://iz.ru/news|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 與大洋洲國家、拉美國家和其他國家的關係 ==
[[File:Vladimir_Putin_in_Cuba_14-17_December_2000-2.jpg|thumb]]主要創立者[[菲德爾·卡斯特羅|菲德爾·卡斯特羅]]，攝於2000年]]
[[File:Putin_in_Malaysia_-_August_5_2003_-_9.jpg|thumb]]与[[马来西亚首相|马来西亚首相]][[马哈迪·莫哈末|马哈迪·莫哈末]]会面交流]]
普京和他的繼任者[[德米特里·阿纳托利耶维奇·梅德韦杰夫|梅德韋傑夫]]一直與[[委內瑞拉總統|委內瑞拉總統]][[查韋斯|查韋斯]]保持友好關係，而普京領導下的俄羅斯自2005年以來已向委內瑞拉出口了超過400億美元的軍火<ref>[http://www.france24.com/en/20080925-russia-nuclear-putin-chavez-nuclear-energy Russia forges nuclear links with Venezuela] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110051027/http://www.france24.com/en/20080925-russia-nuclear-putin-chavez-nuclear-energy |date=2013-11-10 }} france24.com</ref>。2008年9月，俄羅斯派出[[Tu-160轟炸機|Tu-160轟炸機]]到委內瑞拉進行飛行訓練<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/7609577.stm Russian bombers land in Venezuela] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/7609577.stm |date=20100327030514 }} [[BBC|BBC]]</ref>；同年11月，兩國在加勒比地區舉行聯合海軍演習<ref>[http://www.itar-tass.com/eng/level2.html?NewsID=13111604&PageNum=0]{{Dead link|date=March 2012}}</ref>。
 
2007年9月，普京訪問[[印尼|印尼]]，是50年來第一個訪問該國的俄羅斯領導人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://brtsis.com/rrubb.htm |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071012181540/http://brtsis.com/rrubb.htm |archivedate=2007-10-12|title=Russia Courts Indonesia |publisher=Web.archive.org |date=12 October 2007 |accessdate=2011-09-24 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。同月，普京出席了在[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]][[悉尼|悉尼]]召開的[[亞太經合組織|亞太經合組織]]會議，並會見[[澳大利亞總理|澳大利亞總理]][[約翰·霍華德|約翰·霍華德]]，並簽訂了鈾礦貿易協議，是由首位訪問澳大利亞的俄羅斯總統<ref>{{cite news|title=俄澳達成歷史性的核原料貿易協議|url=http://hk.crntt.com/doc/1004/4/4/5/100444509.html?coluid=87&kindid=2521&docid=100444509&mdate=0911123624|newspaper=中國評論通訊社|date=2007-09-07|accessdate=2014-08-02|archive-date=2014-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140810095920/http://hk.crntt.com/doc/1004/4/4/5/100444509.html?coluid=87&kindid=2521&docid=100444509&mdate=0911123624|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2000年12月，普京曾访问古巴，承诺加强双边关系；2014年7月11日，普京开始为期6天的拉美之行，首站访问[[古巴|古巴]]；兩國签署了大约12项合作协议，涉及[[能源|能源]]、[[工业|工业]]、[[医疗|医疗]]和[[防灾|防灾]]等多个领域；俄罗斯又决定减免古巴350多亿美元债务的90%<ref>{{cite news|title=普京会见老卡斯特罗 决定减免古巴90%债务|url=http://news.ifeng.com/a/20140713/41133339_0.shtml|newspaper=北京晨报|date=2014-07-13|accessdate=2014-08-02|archive-date=2014-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808133820/http://news.ifeng.com/a/20140713/41133339_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

